sources.title: America's 60 Greatest Unsolved Mysteries & Crimes (E3,S1)
sources.description:
Was Apollo 11's moon landing a hoax? Did Tom Horn really murder Willie Nickell? Where is the treasure of Dutch Schultz? Were Sacco and Vanzetti innocent? Will the Tylenol murders ever be solved? Where did Wisconsin's Eagle Diamond come from? What killed Harry Houdini?
This compelling documentary series presents a countdown of America's 60 most notorious unsolved mysteries and crimes in a dramatic compilation revealing these unanswered questions in 10 fascinating episodes.
